channel.title: Inner Monologue with Olivia Neill
channel.description: Known for being the internet's bestie and a self-confessed chatterbox with a non-stop inner monologue, YouTuber Olivia Neill will be in your ears every Wednesday. Bringing her unfiltered honesty, each week she'll be unpacking what it’s really like to navigate the world as a 20-year old from Northern Ireland living in London; chatting life online, relationship dramas, friendship and sharing advice and anecdotes in response to your questions and stories. No topic is off limits!Get involved each week on Instagram (@olivianeill) and hit follow so you never miss an episode.Inner Monologue is a Spotify Original produced by Spirit Studios, the producer is Raymond Tannor. For Spotify the Executive Producer is Rhyanna Coleman.
